<D>__{who's brumby?}
<C>__{carter}
<D>__{cliff brumby. ever been to westsea?}
<A>__{keith nods.}
<C>__{carter}
<D>__{ever been into an arcade there and put a penny in the slot machine?}
<C>__{keith}
<D>__{yeah.}
<C>__{carter}
<D>__{ten to one, it belonged to cliff brumby, and like as not the bloody arcade as well. right along the coast. isn't that right, thorpey?}
<A>__{thorpe drags himself painfully to a chair.}
<C>__{carter}
<D>__{where's he living these days?}
<C>__{thorpe}
<D>__{he's got a new place at burnham.}
<C>__{carter}
<D>__{address?}
